                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000a64049cd-cb2c-4279-972d-48a5fb44b6d7" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(R\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a64049cd-cb2c-4279-972d-48a5fb44b6d7"> Gi GKK </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(CGS\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a64049cd-cb2c-4279-972d-48a5fb44b6d7"> G ai‡j </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(He\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a64049cd-cb2c-4279-972d-48a5fb44b6d7"> Gi fi </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(4g\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000a64049cd-cb2c-4279-972d-48a5fb44b6d7 {margin-right: 0.25in;text-align: left;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001a64049cd-cb2c-4279-972d-48a5fb44b6d7 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000007e8cd554-9798-438c-b7f4-e5977a450605" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({C}_{rms}=\sqrt{\frac{3RT}{M}}=\sqrt{\frac{3R\times 300}{4\times {10}^{-3}}}=\sqrt{\frac{900\times 100\times 10}{4}\times R}=150\sqrt{10R}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000017e8cd554-9798-438c-b7f4-e5977a450605"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000007e8cd554-9798-438c-b7f4-e5977a450605 {margin-right: 0.25in;text-align: left;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000017e8cd554-9798-438c-b7f4-e5977a450605 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
